{"_id":"lightsaber-accessory-beckon-call","name":"Beckon Call","type":"weaponUpgrade","img":"icons/svg/amulet.svg","system":{"cost":0,"weight":0,"upgradeSlots":1,"lightsaber":{"category":"accessory","buildDcModifier":0,"compatibleChassis":["standard","double","short","great","pike","shoto","crossguard","dual-phase","dueling","lightwhip","longhandle"]},"description":"<p>A device that allows the wielder to summon a Vehicle using a Slave Circuit. When activated, the vehicle will travel to the wielder's location automatically.</p>","modifiers":[{"type":"VEHICLE_SUMMON"}]},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"lightsaber-accessory-blade-lock","name":"Blade Lock","type":"weaponUpgrade","img":"icons/svg/lock.svg","system":{"cost":0,"weight":0,"upgradeSlots":1,"lightsaber":{"category":"accessory","buildDcModifier":0,"compatibleChassis":["standard","double","short","great","pike","shoto","crossguard","dual-phase","dueling","lightwhip","longhandle"]},"description":"<p>A mechanical lock that secures the blade so it doesn't accidentally deactivate when the Lightsaber is thrown or during combat.</p>","modifiers":[{"type":"BLADE_LOCK"}]},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"lightsaber-accessory-concealed-compartment","name":"Concealed Compartment","type":"weaponUpgrade","img":"icons/svg/chest.svg","system":{"cost":0,"weight":0,"upgradeSlots":1,"lightsaber":{"category":"accessory","buildDcModifier":0,"compatibleChassis":["standard","double","short","great","pike","shoto","crossguard","dual-phase","dueling","lightwhip","longhandle"]},"description":"<p>A secret compartment hidden within the Lightsaber hilt that can store a Fine-sized object (approximately the size of a small tool or lightsaber emitter component).</p>","modifiers":[{"type":"STORAGE_COMPARTMENT","capacity":"fine"}]},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"lightsaber-accessory-electrum-detail","name":"Electrum Detail","type":"weaponUpgrade","img":"icons/svg/jewelry.svg","system":{"cost":0,"weight":0,"upgradeSlots":1,"lightsaber":{"category":"accessory","buildDcModifier":0,"compatibleChassis":["standard","double","short","great","pike","shoto","crossguard","dual-phase","dueling","lightwhip","longhandle"]},"description":"<p>An ornamental symbol of rank and skill, similar to a badge of honor. Crafted from electrum inlay, it signals the wielder's expertise and is often associated with Jedi masters or accomplished warriors.</p>","modifiers":[{"type":"PRESTIGE_MARKER"}]},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"lightsaber-accessory-fiber-cord","name":"Fiber Cord","type":"weaponUpgrade","img":"icons/svg/rope.svg","system":{"cost":0,"weight":0,"upgradeSlots":1,"lightsaber":{"category":"accessory","buildDcModifier":0,"compatibleChassis":["standard","short","shoto","dueling"],"incompatible":["double","lightwhip"]},"description":"<p>A cord tied to the end of the Lightsaber hilt that makes the wielder significantly harder to Disarm. Provides +2 bonus against Disarm attempts.</p>","modifiers":[{"type":"DISARM_RESISTANCE","value":2}]},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"lightsaber-accessory-force-activated","name":"Force-Activated","type":"weaponUpgrade","img":"icons/svg/star.svg","system":{"cost":0,"weight":0,"upgradeSlots":1,"lightsaber":{"category":"accessory","buildDcModifier":0,"compatibleChassis":["standard","double","short","great","pike","shoto","crossguard","dual-phase","dueling","lightwhip","longhandle"]},"description":"<p>The Lightsaber can only be activated through the use of the Force. Non-Force users cannot activate or use this weapon. Requires a Use the Force check (DC 10) to activate.</p>","modifiers":[{"type":"FORCE_ACTIVATION_REQUIRED"}]},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"lightsaber-accessory-interlocking-hilt","name":"Interlocking Hilt","type":"weaponUpgrade","img":"icons/svg/hook.svg","system":{"cost":0,"weight":0,"upgradeSlots":1,"lightsaber":{"category":"accessory","buildDcModifier":0,"compatibleChassis":["standard","short","shoto","dueling","lightwhip"],"incompatible":["double"]},"description":"<p>A hook attached to the end of a single-bladed Lightsaber that allows it to attach to another Lightsaber with this same Accessory, forming a temporary double-bladed configuration or creating a linked weapon system.</p>","modifiers":[{"type":"INTERLOCKING_SYSTEM"}]},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"lightsaber-accessory-pressure-grip","name":"Pressure Grip","type":"weaponUpgrade","img":"icons/svg/gloves.svg","system":{"cost":0,"weight":0,"upgradeSlots":1,"lightsaber":{"category":"accessory","buildDcModifier":0,"compatibleChassis":["standard","double","short","great","pike","shoto","crossguard","dual-phase","dueling","lightwhip","longhandle"]},"description":"<p>An advanced grip mechanism that automatically disables the Lightsaber when it is no longer being held by the wielder's hand. Prevents accidental blade ignition or loss of the weapon if dropped.</p>","modifiers":[{"type":"PRESSURE_ACTIVATED"}]},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"lightsaber-accessory-trapped-grip","name":"Trapped Grip","type":"weaponUpgrade","img":"icons/svg/trap.svg","system":{"cost":0,"weight":0,"upgradeSlots":1,"lightsaber":{"category":"accessory","buildDcModifier":0,"compatibleChassis":["standard","double","short","great","pike","shoto","crossguard","dual-phase","dueling","lightwhip","longhandle"]},"description":"<p>Boobytrap mechanism hidden within the Lightsaber grip. If activated, deals 2d6 damage to the creature triggering the trap. Can be disarmed with a hidden knob or button known only to the creator. Requires a Mechanics check (DC 20) to disarm safely.</p>","modifiers":[{"type":"BOOBYTRAP","damage":"2d6"}]},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"lightsaber-accessory-waterproof-casing","name":"Waterproof Casing","type":"weaponUpgrade","img":"icons/svg/water.svg","system":{"cost":0,"weight":0,"upgradeSlots":1,"lightsaber":{"category":"accessory","buildDcModifier":0,"compatibleChassis":["standard","double","short","great","pike","shoto","crossguard","dual-phase","dueling","lightwhip","longhandle"]},"description":"<p>A specialized protective casing that allows the Lightsaber to function normally while submerged in water or other liquids. Prevents short circuits and corrosion from moisture or saltwater.</p>","modifiers":[{"type":"WATERPROOF"}]},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
